title: Revenue of the Minnesota Vikings ( NFL ) 2001 to 2018
summary: Overall Revenue in million U.S. dollars has increased over the Year.
Revenue in million U.S. dollars is roughly constant from 2004 to 2005, and lastly slightly increasing from 2005 to 2007.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2005 and 2006.
The highest Revenue in million U.S. dollars, of value 195.0 was reached at Year 2007
The lowest Revenue in million U.S. dollars, of value 164.0 was reported at Year 2004
